{"lemma":"مَعِيشَةٌ","slug":"مَعِيشَةٌ","root":"ع.#.ش","root_slug":"ع-_-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَعِيشَة","root":"عيش","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31224"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَاشَ (ʕāša) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"living, subsistence, livelihood"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"way of living"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of عَاشَ (ʕāša)."},"ipa":["/ma.ʕiː.ʃa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31224","headword_ar":"مَعِيشَةٌ","root":"Ey$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaA$a","text_ar":"عَاشَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Victuals, living, sustenance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food and drink by which one lives;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, A, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) whence you say that dates are the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$","text_ar":"عَيْش"},{"kind":"text","text":"of such a family: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that whereby life subsists;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of life"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subsistence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that whereby one lives;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaA$N","text_ar":"مَعَاشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$N","text_ar":"مَعِيشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wherein one lives;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eayo$N","text_ar":"عَيْشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaA$N","text_ar":"مَعَاشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$N","text_ar":"مَعِيشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means of obtaining that whereby one lives:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Is-hák, TA:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earnings, by means of which a man lives;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$N","text_ar":"مَعِيشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAyi$u","text_ar":"مَعَايِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) accord. to general opinion, (Msb,) without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) when formed from the original of the sing., which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoyi$apN","text_ar":"مَعْيِشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEilapN","text_ar":"مَفْعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O;) or because it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaA$a","text_ar":"عَاشَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", so that the measure of the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafaAEilu","text_ar":"مَفَاعِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) but when it is formed from the secondary form of the sing., it is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAy^i$u","text_ar":"مَعَايِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEilapN","text_ar":"مَفْعِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being in this case likened to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylapN","text_ar":"فَعِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaAy^ibu","text_ar":"مَصَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in its sing.] is quiescent; but some of the grammarians hold this latter pl. to be incorrect: (S, O:) all the Basree grammarians hold it to be so: (TA:) or, accord. to some, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$N","text_ar":"مَعِيشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$apN","text_ar":"مَعِيشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mE$","text_ar":"معش"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the pl. in question is therefore of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEaAy^ilu","text_ar":"فَعَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEiy$apN DanokN","text_ar":"مَعِيشَةٌ ضَنْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"punishment of the grave:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) so, accord. to most of the expositors, in the Kur xx. 123: or, as some say, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strait sustenance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the fire of hell."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","A","K","Msb","S","O"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}